{"tid":1431038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國對香港旅遊警示提升至二級","createTime":"2019-08-08T01:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T01:47:53.000Z","uid":13468,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"628e831af328975a8fb157e898036f66e99d83a4","tid":1431038,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:45:30.000Z","msg":"美國對香港旅遊警示提升至二級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國國務院宣布將香港旅遊警示提升至第二級別。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院在當地周一透過網頁宣布，將香港旅遊警示提升至第二級，指香港正出現內亂，自6月9日開始，香港多區持續出現多場大規模政治示威，部分示威和平進行。<br />\n<br />\n但亦部分演變成暴力衝突並已蔓延至社區，這些示威可能在短時間內及無預警下發生，預料情況會持續，呼籲到香港旅遊的美國公民密切注意傳媒報道示威資訊，避免到示威區，對四周環境提高警覺以及保持低調。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358343&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rA2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=7189b70b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358343&h=e12f6dc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358343</a>"},{"pid":"00e5b8d45bbea27c07fdaf474ff35f161f4ce824","tid":1431038,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:47:49.000Z","msg":"Thanks for ur attention<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1171704cc1180866689adb3ce2b1f2980493f9","tid":1431038,"uid":101092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:47:53.000Z","msg":"老美呢期好落力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又貨幣操控國 又旅警 離光復不遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}